      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, form Suleym Al Fara’a who said, ",
          "‘Amir Al-Momineen<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘<span class=\"iTxt\">Al-Noura</span> is a cleanser’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Sulaym al-Farra’ who has said the following: “’Amir al-Mu’minin, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, Time is a cleansing (agent).”’ "
        ]
